oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Unaka Springs, Deaderick Family, 1905
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: unknown
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Family group at Unaka Springs, 1905. Seated on grass: Three children of C.C. Deaderick: Tom, Elizabeth and Alfred. Seated: Mrs. H.M. Deaderick, Mrs. J.M. Brown, Mr. and Mrs. A.V. Deaderick, Miss Mary Clarkson, Mrs. and Mr. Chas. C. Deaderick. Standing: H.M. Deaderick, Adeline Brown, Fanny Brown, Mary E. Deaderick, George Deaderick, Aunt Eliza Conrad, Annie Deaderick, Clarkson Deaderick.
